  "text": "It is more difficult to compare the sensorimotor paradigm here with the previous work [CITATION_1] . In the present study a simple, sequential finger-tapping paradigm was presented and there was only one regressor of interest in the present analysis. By contrast, the previous study used a motor learning and reaction task that was part of a more complicated multivariate analysis [CITATION_2] .",
